    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Coiled springs that determine the time of vibration of balance wheels, with which they work to regulate the progress of the hands on timepieces.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
